        "subject": "LU-4746 libcfs: Use Linux kernel current_umask() function",
        "message": "LU-4746 libcfs: Use Linux kernel current_umask() function\n\nLustre not using kernel current_umask() function breaks GRSecurity\numask handling\n\nReplaces current->fs->umask with more secure current_umask() function\n\nThis version is for Lustre 2.4.2\n\nChange-Id: If1ca9d3e223ad47c14e367b34f63bc47d1f14aca\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Prout <ajprout@hotmail.com>\nSigned-off-by: Cliff White <cliffwhi@intel.com>\n"
